articles.title: Division 7 - Rock Lobsters overtook Fiordlands 2 - 1
articles.content:
For Rock Lobsters, Phineas Samuelson ground out 24 Saves. John Millard had 1 Goal, 1 Point. Emily Kmiec broke out 1 Goal, 1 Point. Phineas Samuelson had a great game to get 2nd Star. John Millard was awarded 3rd Star. For Fiordlands, Josh Thompson broke out 18 Saves. Samuel Eastham ground out 1 Goal, 1 Point. Visit the game page

Catch the Replay on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VnxqObp-pgg

Want to save any good moments from the game? You can curate highlights for your team and players by clicking the "Highlights" button on the game page and setting a start and stop time for your highlight. You can even tag players so they can find their highlights on their player pages.
